'''-{zh-cn:安伯·奥古丝塔·拉德;zh-hk:盧綺婷;zh-tw:安珀·奧古斯塔·魯德;}-'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mnre.gov.in/file-manager/annual-report/2015-2016/EN/Chapter%2011/chapter_11.htm#6|title=Annual Report|publisher=[[Ministry_of_New_and_Renewable_Energy|Ministry of New and Renewable Energy]]|accessdate=31 October 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008174003/http://mnre.gov.in/file-manager/annual-report/2015-2016/EN/Chapter%2011/chapter_11.htm#6|archive-date=2017-10-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Amber Augusta Rudd}}，{{bd|1963年|8月1日||catIdx=R}}），英國政治人物、前保守黨党员、現任[[東薩塞克斯郡|東薩塞克斯郡]][[黑斯廷斯和拉伊_(英國國會選區)|黑斯廷斯和拉伊選區]][[國會議員|下議院議員]]、曾於2015至2016年间任{{le|能源和气候变化大臣（英国）|Secretary of State for Energy and Climate Change|能源和气候变化大臣}}、2016年7月至2018年4月担任英国内政大臣及2018年1月至4月兼任婦女及平等事務大臣。拉德是英国历史上第三位女性[[內政大臣_(英國)|内政大臣]]，第五位担任[[內閣重臣|內閣重臣]]的女性，也是[[二战|二战]]后英国政坛晋升至內閣重臣速度最快的政治人物之一，<ref>{{cite news |author=Andrew Marr, Amber Rudd |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/bsp/hi/pdfs/11091604.pdf |title=ANDREW MARR SHOW, AMBER RUDD (transcript) |publisher=BBC |date=11 September 2016 |accessdate=11 June 2017 |archive-date=2017-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809002454/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/bsp/hi/pdfs/11091604.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>但之後因[[疾風世代|疾風世代]]醜聞而辭職。同年重新進入內閣，並於2018至2019年間先後就任婦女及平等事務大臣和就業及退休保障大臣，至2019年9月因不滿[[莊漢生|莊漢生]]首相的硬脫歐立場而辭職並退黨。

== 早年生活和教育 ==
安珀·拉德1963年8月1日<ref>{{cite news|url=http://platinumbusinessmagazine.com/amber-rudd-the-indefinable-politician/|work=Platinum Business|title=Amber Rudd – The Indefinable Politician|accessdate=31 October 2017|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107021110/http://platinumbusinessmagazine.com/amber-rudd-the-indefinable-politician/|dead-url=no}}</ref>出生在伦敦上流社区[[马里波恩|马里波恩]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.freebmd.org.uk/cgi/information.pl?cite=gn5Gp%2BfpWSORe1MecPHO4A&scan=1|title=Index entry|accessdate=25 June 2017|work=FreeBMD|publisher=ONS}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theargus.co.uk/news/elections/general_election_2010/constituencies/33.hastings___rye/candidates/2676._amber_rudd |title=Amber Rudd |work=[[The_Argus_(Brighton)|The Argus]] |accessdate=9 May 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523034521/http://www.theargus.co.uk/news/elections/general_election_2010/constituencies/33.hastings___rye/candidates/2676._amber_rudd/ |archive-date=2015-05-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>是股票经纪人托尼·拉德（1924-2017）和治安官埃瑟娜·菲茨杰拉德（1929-2008）的四女儿，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.conservativehome.com/profiles/2015/05/profile-amber-rudd-a-true-believer-in-climate-change.html|title=Profile: Amber Rudd, a true believer in climate change|trans_title=简介：安珀·拉德气候变化的真正信徒|work=conservativehome|date=20 May 2015|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211144205/https://www.conservativehome.com/profiles/2015/05/profile-amber-rudd-a-true-believer-in-climate-change.html|archive-date=2018-12-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>后者是自由党政治人物{{le|约翰·菲茨杰拉德,菲茨杰拉德男爵|John FitzGerald, Baron FitzGerald}}的孙女。<ref>Burke's Peerage, Baronetage and Knightage 2003, vol. 1, pg 271</ref><ref>Burke's Peerage, Baronetage and Knightage 2003, vol. 3, pg 3044</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thepeerage.com/p68480.htm#i684791|title=Person Page|website=Thepeerage.com|accessdate=23 June 2017|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129233107/http://www.thepeerage.com/p68480.htm#i684791|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.conservativehome.com/profiles/2015/05/profile-amber-rudd-a-true-believer-in-climate-change.html|title=Profile: Amber Rudd, a true believer in climate change|work=conservativehome|date=20 May 2015|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211144205/https://www.conservativehome.com/profiles/2015/05/profile-amber-rudd-a-true-believer-in-climate-change.html|archive-date=2018-12-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>她带给了拉德[[查理二世_(英格兰)|查理二世]]及其情妇[[芭芭拉·帕門爾|克里夫蘭女公爵]]的血统。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b07rh0xv|title=Amber Rudd, Profile - BBC Radio 4|website=BBC|accessdate=24 May 2017|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225124515/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b07rh0xv|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3705013/Her-Majesty-Home-Secretary-Amber-Rudd-direct-descendant-King-Charles-II-mistress-known-beauty-promiscuity-foul-temper.html|title=Amber Rudd a direct descendant of King Charles II and his mistress|publisher=|accessdate=24 May 2017|archive-date=2017-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318005129/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3705013/Her-Majesty-Home-Secretary-Amber-Rudd-direct-descendant-King-Charles-II-mistress-known-beauty-promiscuity-foul-temper.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>二人婚姻关系维持了56年。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/health/3415618/Planning-for-death-The-secrets-of-a-happy-ending.html|2=|title=Planning for death: The secrets of a happy ending|date=10 November 2008|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921090540/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/health/3415618/Planning-for-death-The-secrets-of-a-happy-ending.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
拉德的兄弟是公共关系管理业者罗兰·拉德，工党支持者、<ref name=ST>"Energy secretary burns with ambition for other women", Tim Shipman, ''[[The_Sunday_Times|The Sunday Times]]'', 17 May 2015, p. 17.</ref>{{le|新欧洲商业|Business for New Europe}}主席；她的姐姐名为阿曼达，妹妹名为梅丽莎。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Changing face of Amber|trans_title=拉德的变脸术|last=Lo Dico|first=Joy|date=18 May 2015|work=[[London_Evening_Standard|London Evening Standard]]|page=17|access-date=|via=}}</ref>

拉德在[[格洛斯特郡|格洛斯特郡]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Norwood|first=Graham|url=http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/style/homes_and_gardens/Move/article1614309.ece|title=Highly fancied|trans_title=高度的空想|work=The Sunday Times|location=London|date=2 October 2015|accessdate=6 December 2015|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325143351/http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/style/homes_and_gardens/Move/article1614309.ece|dead-url=no}}{{subscription required}}</ref>的{{le|切尔滕纳姆女子学院|Cheltenham Ladies' College}}接受教育，1979年至1981年在伦敦的独立走读女校{{le|伦敦女王学院|Queen's College, London}}就读，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.qcl.org.uk/mobile/former-pupils.php|title=Former pupils – Amber Rudd|trans_title=拉德的求学之路|work={{le|伦敦女王学院|Queen's College, London}}|accessdate=8 June 2015|archive-date=2019-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190907132502/http://www.qcl.org.uk/mobile/former-pupils.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>随后前往[[爱丁堡大学|爱丁堡大学]]学习历史。

== 商务职业生涯 ==

大学毕业后，拉德加入[[摩根大通|摩根大通]]，在纽约和伦敦两地工作。<br />
她曾帮助电影《[[四个婚礼和一个葬礼|四个婚礼和一个葬礼]]》寻找演员，被称为“贵族协调员”，并在电影中客串了一个角色。<ref name=ST/><ref name="www.ft.com" />

1988年1月，拉德24岁时成为投资公司洛德斯通有限公司的主管，接替其姐姐和姐夫。<ref>{{cite news | last = Hotten | first = Russell | title = DTI probe into Norton looks at Rudd links (CORRECTED) | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/dti-probe-into-norton-looks-at-rudd-links-corrected-1539583.html | work = [[独立报|独立报]] | date = 10 August 1992 | accessdate = 3 June 2017 | archive-date = 2019-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190604075436/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/dti-probe-into-norton-looks-at-rudd-links-corrected-1539583.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>1995年，洛德斯通公司在[[秘鲁|秘鲁]]开展锌矿开采业务，拉德成为这家公司的主管和大股东，该公司从未真正盈利，1999年被蒙蒂塞洛公司兼并。拉德在1999年至2000年期间担任蒙蒂塞洛公司的联合主任。洛德斯通公司在2001年被变卖；蒙蒂塞洛则在2003年。<ref>{{cite news|title=Amber Rudd and Monticello: an ill-fated step in a complicated career|trans_title=拉德：命途多舛的商业职涯|url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/sep/21/amber-rudd-monticello-ill-fated-step-complicated-career-bahamas-leaks|4=|work=The Guardian|accessdate=31 October 2016|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030833/https://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/sep/21/amber-rudd-monticello-ill-fated-step-complicated-career-bahamas-leaks|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1998年至2000年，拉德还是两家位于[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]的资产配置基金和资产配置管理公司的主管。<ref name=guardian21092016>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/sep/21/bahamas-leaks-reveal-amber-rudd-involvement-offshore-firms|title=Leaks reveal Amber Rudd's involvement in Bahamas offshore firms|trans_title=泄漏揭露拉德参与巴哈马离岸公司|first=David|last=Pegg|first2=Holly|last2=Watt|date=21 September 2016|work=The Guardian|accessdate=21 September 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108134049/http://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/sep/21/bahamas-leaks-reveal-amber-rudd-involvement-offshore-firms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-37432666|title=Leak reveals Amber Rudd's links to offshore investment funds – BBC News|trans_title=泄露的文件显示拉德与离岸公司的联系|date=21 September 2016|work=[[BBC_Online|BBC Online]]|accessdate=21 September 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108204419/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-37432666|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 政坛生涯 ==

在[[2005年英国大选|2005年的大选]]中，拉德是工党占据的{{le|利物浦加利斯顿选区|Liverpool Garston (UK Parliament constituency)}}的保守党候选人。

她的名字随后被有争议的添加到旨在增加保守党席位的{{le|A名单|A-List (Conservative)}}中，2006年被派往[[黑斯廷斯和拉伊_(英國國會選區)|黑斯廷斯和拉伊选区]]参选，2007年搬到黑斯廷斯旧城。<ref name="www.ft.com" />在[[2010年英国大选|2010年5月的大选]]中，拉德在黑斯廷斯和拉伊选区以1,993张多數票击败[[工党_(英国)|工党]]议员{{le|迈克尔·福斯特（政治家）|Michael Foster|迈克尔·福斯特}}而当选。不久之后，拉德成为{{le|下议院环境、食品和农村事务专责委员会|Environment, Food and Rural Affairs Select Committee}}的保守党成员。

拉德是国会女性外阴残割问题委员会副主席，该委员会反对女性外阴残割，并呼吁在国内采取更严厉的法律处罚。她作为性别平等{{le|议员联盟|All-party parliamentary group}}的主席倡导性别平等事业，<ref>{{cite web|title=All-Party Parliamentary Group for Sex Equality|trans_title=性别平等跨党派议员小组|url=http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm/cmallparty/register/sex-equality.htm|website=Parliament UK|accessdate=30 March 2015|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926025333/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm/cmallparty/register/sex-equality.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>并发表了一份关于妇女在工作中不平等待遇的报告。拉德主持了一项针对意外怀孕的跨党派调查，呼吁在所有中学开展法定的性常识教育。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Stratton|first1=Allegra|title=MPs call for compulsory relationship education|trans_title=议员们呼吁强制性启蒙教育|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-20785049|accessdate=30 March 2015|publisher=BBC News|date=19 December 2012|archive-date=2018-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181110165952/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-20785049|dead-url=no}}</ref>她还呼吁在[[英国内阁|内阁]]中应有更多女成员。<ref name="Roberts">{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2012/nov/25/women-equality-gender-gap-bishops | title=Has the drive towards sexual equality gone into reverse? | trans_title=性别平等运动已经偏离初衷？ | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date=25 November 2012 | accessdate=11 May 2015 | last=Roberts | first=Yvonne | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003140/http://www.theguardian.com/society/2012/nov/25/women-equality-gender-gap-bishops | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2012年9月，她成为[[英國財政大臣|财政大臣]][[喬治·奧斯本|乔治·奥斯本]]的{{le|國會私人秘書|Parliamentary Private Secretary}}。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hastingsobserver.co.uk/news/local-news/amber-rudd-mp-in-new-role-with-chancellor-1-4255204|title=Amber Rudd MP in new role with Chancellor|trans_title=拉德议员获得财政大臣身边的新职位|work=[[Hastings_&_St._Leonards_Observer|Hastings Observer]]|date=13 September 2012|accessdate=12 December 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023041212/http://www.hastingsobserver.co.uk/news/local-news/amber-rudd-mp-in-new-role-with-chancellor-1-4255204|archive-date=2012-10-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2013年10月，改任[[党鞭长_(英国)|政府助理党鞭]]。 2014年7月，拉德被任命为{{link-en|能源及氣候變化部|Department of Energy and Climate Change}}负责氣候變化的政务次官。<ref name="Daily Telegraph 15 July 2014">{{cite news |last= Gosden |first= Emily |title= Cabinet reshuffle: Chancellor's allies Matt Hancock and Amber Rudd join energy department |trans_title= 内阁改组：财政大臣的盟友马特·汉考克和安珀·拉德加入能源部 |url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/energy/10969165/Cabinet-reshuffle-Chancellors-allies-Matt-Hancock-and-Amber-Rudd-join-energy-department.html |date= 15 July 2014 |newspaper= [[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |location= London |accessdate= 17 July 2015 |archive-date= 2019-06-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190606142659/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/energy/10969165/Cabinet-reshuffle-Chancellors-allies-Matt-Hancock-and-Amber-Rudd-join-energy-department.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="BBC 15 July 2014">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-28303854 |title=Reshuffle at-a-glance: In, out and moved about |trans_title=改组一览：去、留和调动 |date=15 July 2014 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=17 July 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115200043/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-28303854 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 能源和气候变化大臣 ===

在[[2015年英國大選|2015年大选]]之后，她获得了扩大了在自己选区的多数优势，被提拔为能源和气候变化大臣。<ref>{{cite web|title=08 May 2015 Parliamentary Election – Results|trans_title=2015年5月8日大选结果|url=http://www.hastings.gov.uk/decisions_democracy/voting_petitioning_having_your_say/elections_voting/electionresults/?elecdate=07052015&electype=general|website=council web site|publisher=Hastings Borough Council|accessdate=8 May 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518072720/http://www.hastings.gov.uk/decisions_democracy/voting_petitioning_having_your_say/elections_voting/electionresults/?elecdate=07052015&electype=general|archivedate=2015年5月18日}}</ref><ref name="BBC News 11 May 2015">{{cite web| title= Cabinet reshuffle: Amber Rudd and Sajid Javid promoted| trans_title= 内阁改组：安珀·拉德和萨吉德·贾亚德被提拔入阁| url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/election-2015-32683868| date= 11 May 2015| publisher= BBC News| accessdate= 9 July 2015| archive-date= 2020-12-04| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201204065629/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/election-2015-32683868| dead-url= no}}</ref>同年5月她成为[[英国枢密院|枢密院]]成员。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://privycouncil.independent.gov.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Privy-Council-business-and-order-14-may-2015.pdf |format=PDF |title=Business Transacted and Order Approved at the Privy Council Held by the Queen at Buckingham Palace |trans_title=枢密院商业交易和订单批准由女王在白金汉宫举行 |date=14 May 2015 |website=Privycouncil.independent.gov.uk |accessdate=3 January 2017 |archive-date=2020-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623160226/https://privycouncil.independent.gov.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Privy-Council-business-and-order-14-may-2015.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年11月，她建议英国剩余的燃煤发电厂在2025年全部关闭，2023年时开始限制使用。“我们需要建立适用于21世纪新的能源基础设施”。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Rudd|first1=Amber|title=Secretary of State for Energy and Climate Change|trans_title=能源和气候变化大臣|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-34851718|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=24 November 2015|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220173149/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-34851718|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年11月，一封泄露的信件显示，政府根本没有将{{le|强制性可再生能源目标|Mandatory renewable energy target}}提上议事日程，{{le|生态学家杂志|The_Ecologist}}批评拉德故意误导国会。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tickell|first1=Oliver|title=Leaked letter: Rudd admits 25% green energy undershoot, misled Parliament|trans_title=泄露的信：拉德承认25％的绿色能源未达到预定目标，误导议会|url=http://www.theecologist.org/News/news_analysis/2986190/leaked_letter_rudd_admits_25_green_energy_undershoot_misled_parliament.html|website=[[The_Ecologist|The Ecologist]]|accessdate=10 November 2015|ref=Leak|archive-date=2018-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180802234711/http://www.theecologist.org/News/news_analysis/2986190/leaked_letter_rudd_admits_25_green_energy_undershoot_misled_parliament.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年7月，[[地球之友|地球之友]]的克雷格·本内特指责拉德想要应对气候变化的声明十分虚伪，而他主张，“废除低碳政策的框架并在国会上下两院仔细组织跨党派协议。”拉德答复说：“政府支持的目的是使能源技术最终能靠自己的双脚走路，不鼓励永久依赖补贴”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-33638495%20Rudd%20criticised%20ahead%20of%20climate%20speech|title=Energy Secretary Amber Rudd criticised ahead of climate speech|trans_title=能源大臣回击有关气候变化应对不利的言论|authorlink=Roger Harrabin|first=Roger|last=Harrabin|work=BBC News|date=24 July 2015|accessdate=7 December 2015}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-35010333|title=COP21: UK under fire on climate policy|trans_title=第21届联合国气候变化大会：英国受气候政策的影响|first=Roger|last=Harrabin|work=BBC News|date=6 December 2015|accessdate=7 December 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108100531/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-35010333|dead-url=no}}</ref>

拉德还受首相[[戴维·卡梅伦|卡梅伦]]指示参加了[[英国独立电视台|英国独立电视台]]关于[[英国脱欧|脱欧公投]]的电视辩论，以工党影子内阁重要成员[[安吉拉·伊格尔|安吉拉·伊格尔]]和苏格兰首席部长[[尼古拉·斯特金|尼古拉·斯特金]]为盟友，与脱欧派的伦敦市前市长[[鲍里斯·约翰逊|鲍里斯·约翰逊]]、自己的副手[[安德里亞·利德森|安德里亚·利德索姆]]等交锋，对约翰逊批评近乎人身攻击的地步，她说：“（鲍里斯·约翰逊）应该看看数字，不过我觉得鲍里斯关心的数字应该只有10号吧……他虽是党内要人，但他不是那种夜生活后，能让人放心送自己回家的人”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/amber-rudd-boris-johnson-theresa-may-cabinet-home-secretary-a7136371.html|title=Amber Rudd on Boris Johnson: 'You can't trust him to take you home at the end of an evening'|trans_title=安珀·拉德评价鲍里斯·约翰逊：他不是那种能让人放心送自己回家的人|first=Samuel|last=Osborne|work=The Independent|date=14 July 2016|accessdate=22 January 2016|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130111502/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/amber-rudd-boris-johnson-theresa-may-cabinet-home-secretary-a7136371.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 内政大臣 ===
[[File:Woody_Johnson_and_HS_Amber_Rudd_meeting.jpg|thumb]]
[[特蕾莎·梅|特蕾莎·梅]]成为[[英国首相|联合王国首相]]后，任命拉德为内政大臣，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.itv.com/news/update/2016-07-13/amber-rudd-appointed-new-home-secretary/|title=Amber Rudd appointed new Home Secretary|trans_title=拉德被任命为内政大臣|website=Itv.com|accessdate=3 January 2017|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108092847/https://www.itv.com/news/update/2016-07-13/amber-rudd-appointed-new-home-secretary/|dead-url=no}}</ref>拉德成为第三位女内政大臣。使她成为继[[玛格丽特·撒切尔|玛格丽特·撒切尔]]、[[玛格丽特·贝克特|玛格丽特·贝克特]]、[[雅基·史密斯|雅基·史密斯]]、[[特蕾莎·梅|特蕾莎·梅]]之后第五位女性国务重臣。

在2016年保守党年会上，拉德提议应该强制公司公示他们雇佣了多少外国工人，商业领袖说这个提议是分裂和破坏性的。该建议的公布是政府减少净移民和鼓励企业雇用英国人的一个关键。然而，商业资深人士警告说，该计划是负责任的雇主“完全厌恶”的，并将损害英国经济，因为英国工人不能填补的技能上的空白。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/oct/05/government-faces-backlash-from-business-leaders-over-foreign-workers|title=Amber Rudd faces backlash from businesses over foreign workers|trans_title=拉德面临外国工人的反弹|work=The Guardian|first=Rowena|last=Mason|date=5 October 2016|accessdate=12 October 2016|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227050750/https://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/oct/05/government-faces-backlash-from-business-leaders-over-foreign-workers|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年10月，拉德否定了澳大利亚公民在英国脱欧盟后应该更容易获得在英国的生活和工作的机会的呼吁，尽管[[英国外交大臣|外交大臣]]鲍里斯·约翰逊和澳大利亚外长[[朱莉·毕晓普|朱莉·毕晓普]]都这样呼吁。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/oct/04/no-plans-to-make-it-easier-for-australians-to-enter-uk-home-secretary-says|title=UK has 'no plans' to make it easier for Australians to enter after Brexit|trans_title=英国没有计划使澳大利亚人在脱欧后更容易进入英国|work=The Guardian|author=Press Association|date=4 October 2016|accessdate=11 December 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108140152/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/oct/04/no-plans-to-make-it-easier-for-australians-to-enter-uk-home-secretary-says|dead-url=no}}</ref>她还驳斥了英国离开欧盟时将和澳大利亚建立公民之间的[[出入境自由|出入境自由]]区的想法，[[澳大利亚总理|澳大利亚前总理]][[托尼·阿博特|托尼·阿博特]]支持这一措施，并说：“没有增加澳大利亚移民的计划...所以我想不到任何改变。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/world/amber-rudd-rules-out-australians-having-easier-immigration-to-uk-after-brexit-20161003-gru3ev.html|title=Amber Rudd rules out Australians having easier immigration to UK after Brexit|trans_title=拉德排除了澳大利亚人在Brexit后更容易移民到英国|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|first=Latika|last=Bourke|date=4 October 2016|accessdate=11 December 2016|archive-date=2017-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816014114/http://www.smh.com.au/world/amber-rudd-rules-out-australians-having-easier-immigration-to-uk-after-brexit-20161003-gru3ev.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2016年10月，拉德决定不再调查1984年奥格里夫矿工罢工事件，她说：“我没有足够证据发起依法审查或独立调查”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/10/31/battle-of-orgreave-home-secretary-to-announce-decision-on-public/|title=Amber Rudd declares there will be no inquiry into the Battle of Orgreave|trans_title=拉德声明不再调查1984年奥格里夫罢工事件|work=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=3 January 2017|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203234939/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/10/31/battle-of-orgreave-home-secretary-to-announce-decision-on-public/|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{why?|date=December 2016}}

2017年1月，拉德在推特上传了自己参加纪念犹太大屠杀活动的照片，并表示“我们永不忘记。”两个星期后，她叫停了旨在为孤儿难民提供避难所的2016年移民法修正案（杜布斯修正案）。记者{{le|谭雅·戈德|Tanya Gold}}在《新政治家》杂志撰文评价那条推文“充其量只能算活动了一下手指，往坏里说就是例行公事的公关活动。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/culture/2017/03/smile-auschwitz-selfie-why-holocaust-memorials-have-failed|title=Smile for the Auschwitz selfie: why Holocaust memorials have failed|work=The New Statesman|accessdate=1 September 2017|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920183724/https://www.newstatesman.com/culture/2017/03/smile-auschwitz-selfie-why-holocaust-memorials-have-failed|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年大选后拉德虽留任内政大臣，但在其选区的多数票下降到只有346张，这可能会影响她的政治前途。<ref>{{cite news | last = Ward | first = Victoria | title = Home Secretary Amber Rudd clings on with a slim majority | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/06/09/could-home-secretary-amber-rudd-lose-seat/ | work = [[Daily_Telegraph|Daily Telegraph]] | date = 9 June 2017 | accessdate = 13 June 2017 | archive-date = 2021-02-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210214070909/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/06/09/could-home-secretary-amber-rudd-lose-seat/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2017年8月，拉德回复了一封冒充最近上任的[[唐宁街通讯总监|唐宁街通讯总监]]{{le|罗比·吉布|Robbie Gibb}}的恶作剧电子邮件，称“积极的消息即将到来”。恶作剧者把邮件发给了拉德公开的国会电子邮件地址，但拉德用她的私人电子邮件回复，这是不安全的。<ref>{{cite news|last=Booth|first=Robert|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/aug/09/amber-rudd-latest-to-fall-victim-to-email-hoaxer-using-fake-account|title=Amber Rudd latest to fall victim to email hoaxer using fake account|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=9 August 2017|accessdate=10 August 2017|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111193501/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/aug/09/amber-rudd-latest-to-fall-victim-to-email-hoaxer-using-fake-account|dead-url=no}}</ref>

