<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/amber-rudd-boris-johnson-brexit-latest-back-seat-driving-theresa-may-a7951196.html|title=Amber Rudd accuses Boris Johnson of 'back-seat driving' Brexit process|date=17 September 2017|publisher=|accessdate=8 October 2017|archive-date=2017-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917121154/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/amber-rudd-boris-johnson-brexit-latest-back-seat-driving-theresa-may-a7951196.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

