==== 非法拘留和驱逐寻求庇护者 ====

2017年8月30日星期三，[[英格蘭及威爾斯高等法院|高等法院]]举行了一次紧急听证会，审查拉德为期四周的推迟从英国拘留中心释放在利比亚监狱遭受酷刑的寻求庇护者的情况。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scottishlegal.com/2017/08/24/high-court-judge-criticises-amber-rudd-over-delay-in-release-of-torture-survivor/|title=High Court judge criticises Amber Rudd over delay in release of torture survivor|date=24 August 2017|work=Scottish Legal News|accessdate=1 September 2017|archive-date=2017-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930112835/https://www.scottishlegal.com/2017/08/24/high-court-judge-criticises-amber-rudd-over-delay-in-release-of-torture-survivor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>有人表示担心，内政大臣未能就延迟释放该名男子提供令人满意的解释。拉德也没有为该男子提供出庭律师，而只提供了事务律师，主持听证会的法官认为这“不可思议”。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/aug/23/judge-amber-rudd-orders-torture-victim-asylum-seeker-detention|title=Judge condemns Amber Rudd for ignoring orders to release torture victim|first=Diane|last=Taylor|date=23 August 2017|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2017-11-15|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112005215/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/aug/23/judge-amber-rudd-orders-torture-victim-asylum-seeker-detention|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年9月14日，《卫报》报道，拉德已授权将萨米姆·比扎德驱逐到[[喀布尔|喀布尔]]，违反了早先的一项禁止她这样做的裁决，原因是[[塔利班|塔利班]]一直威胁比扎德的生命。<ref name="theguardian.com">{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/sep/14/home-secretary-ignores-court-order-sends-asylum-seeker-kabul-samim-bigzad|work=The Guardian|title=Home secretary ignores court order and sends asylum seeker to Kabul|first=Diane|last=Taylor|date=14 September 2017|accessdate=2017-11-15|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031427/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/sep/14/home-secretary-ignores-court-order-sends-asylum-seeker-kabul-samim-bigzad|dead-url=no}}</ref>高等法院法官认定拉德三次[[藐视法庭|藐视法庭]]，之后她无视命令将比扎德遣送出英国。<ref name="theguardian.com"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lawcareers.net/Information/News/Amber-Rudd-in-contempt-of-court-for-ignoring-judges-order-not-to-deport-asylum|work=LawCareers.net|title=Amber Rudd in contempt of court for ignoring judge’s order not to deport asylum seeker to Afghanistan|publisher=|accessdate=8 October 2017|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610000906/https://www.lawcareers.net/Information/News/Amber-Rudd-in-contempt-of-court-for-ignoring-judges-order-not-to-deport-asylum|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2017/sep/19/home-secretary-courts-amber-rudd-deport-samim-bigzad|title=If Amber Rudd can’t explain why she defied the courts, she should go - Charles Falconer|first=Charles|last=Falconer|date=19 September 2017|accessdate=2017-11-15|archive-date=2021-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305175654/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2017/sep/19/home-secretary-courts-amber-rudd-deport-samim-bigzad|dead-url=no}}</ref>一位不愿吐露姓名的大律师告诉《独立报》，拉德可能因违抗高等法院的指示而被判处监禁。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/samim-bigzad-deportation-afghanistan-asylum-seeker-amber-rudd-home-office-violate-court-order-kabul-a7959756.html|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|title=Samim Bigzad: Afghan asylum seeker at heart of case that 'could jail' Amber Rudd speaks out|first=Lizzie|last=Dearden|date=21 September 2017|accessdate=2017-11-15|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023110/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/samim-bigzad-deportation-afghanistan-asylum-seeker-amber-rudd-home-office-violate-court-order-kabul-a7959756.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 网络严打 ====
{{main|英国的互联网审查}}
2017年10月，拉德宣布政府采取行动打击英国公民被允许在互联网上查看的内容。作为反“网络极端化”行动的一部分，她表示，政府将会收紧法律，让英国公民反复阅读某些被禁止的互联网内容可能会面临长达15年的牢狱之灾。她说：“我想确保那些在网上查看卑劣的[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]内容的人，包括[[聖戰者|圣战]]网站、[[極右派|极右]]宣传和制造{{le|互联网炸弹制作步骤|Bomb-making instructions on the internet|炸弹}}的步骤，都要面对法律的全力制裁。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/oct/03/amber-rudd-viewers-of-online-terrorist-material-face-15-years-in-jail|title=Amber Rudd: viewers of online terrorist material face 15 years in jail|date=3 October 2017|work=The Guardian|accessdate=4 October 2017|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201090510/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/oct/03/amber-rudd-viewers-of-online-terrorist-material-face-15-years-in-jail|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/terrorist-propaganda-criminal-offence-new-law-amber-rudd-streaming-watching-extremist-material-isis-a7979986.html|title=Watching terrorist propaganda online to become a criminal offence, says Tory Home Secretary Amber Rudd|date=3 October 2017|work=The Independent|accessdate=4 October 2017|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213220244/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/terrorist-propaganda-criminal-offence-new-law-amber-rudd-streaming-watching-extremist-material-isis-a7979986.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 辭職 ====
2018年4月，盧綺婷捲入驅逐「[[疾風世代|疾風世代]]」移民風波，被反對派要求引咎辭職。盧綺婷承認因為自己的疏忽而誤導了國會議員，于2018年4月29日宣布辞去内政大臣职务。<ref>{{Cite news|title=「重臣」涉醜聞請辭 梅首相壓力或剛開始|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-43952244|newspaper=BBC News 中文|accessdate=2022-04-06|language=zh-hant}}</ref>

=== 重返內閣 ===
2018年11月，盧綺婷因[[麥蔚宜|麥蔚宜]]以不滿脫歐方案為由辭去就業及退休保障大臣而獲得重返內閣的機會。

2019年7月，鮑里斯·約翰遜在黨內選舉擊敗[[侯俊偉|侯俊偉]]，接替文翠珊成為黨魁兼首相。但支持侯俊偉拜相的她不但在新內閣中獲保留就業及退休保障大臣的職務，更添上婦女及平等事務大臣的職務，令她第二度擔任此職。但一個多月後，隨着二十多名同黨議員因議會投票支持奪取莊漢生議會控制權而遭開除黨籍，選自反對脫歐選區的盧綺婷也因其反對硬脫歐以及對莊漢生開除二十多名保守黨議員黨籍不滿，於數日後辭去內閣職務並退黨<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-09/08/c_1124973012.htm |title=英国就业与养老金大臣宣布辞职 |access-date=2019-09-08 |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805095709/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-09/08/c_1124973012.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2019-09/15423557.html?agt=15422 约翰逊再遭“背叛”：英国就业及退休保障大臣安伯·拉德辞职、退党]</ref>。一個多月後，她宣布隨該年12月大選，不再爭取連任議員。

== 地方事务 ==

拉德一直积极参与黑斯廷斯当地捕鱼船队的运动。她在处女演讲中倡导欧盟[[共同漁業政策|共同渔业政策]]的批发改革。<ref>{{cite web|title=Fairer deal for fishermen in maiden speech|trans_title=首次演讲中呼吁公平对待渔民|url=http://amberrudd.co.uk/news/better-transport-a-fairer-deal-for-fishermen-in-maiden-speech/|website=Amanda Rudd|accessdate=30 March 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130103080238/http://amberrudd.co.uk/news/better-transport-a-fairer-deal-for-fishermen-in-maiden-speech/|archivedate=2013年1月3日}}</ref>

拉德也成功争取连接黑斯廷斯和贝克希尔之间道路的修建。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.planningresource.co.uk/news/1176975 |title=Final funding approval for Bexhill-Hastings link road |trans_title=贝克希尔-黑斯廷斯连接道路的最终融资批准 |publisher=Planningresource.co.uk |date=3 April 2013 |accessdate=18 May 2015 |archive-date=2021-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108131057/https://www.planningresource.co.uk/article/1176975/final-funding-approval-bexhill-hastings-link-road |dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年初，政府在十年呼吁之后终于开工建设这条道路，而在此之前拉德一直在领导一项名为“完成连接”的为建设道路争取资金的运动。<ref>{{cite web|title=Complete the Link|trans_title=完成连接道路|url=http://amberrudd.co.uk/news/complete-the-link/|website=Amber Rudd|accessdate=30 March 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130801120053/http://amberrudd.co.uk/news/complete-the-link/|archivedate=2013年8月1日}}</ref>

2013年4月，[[金融时报_(英国)|金融时报]]一篇关于拉德的简介中引用她的话<ref name="www.ft.com">{{cite news |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/97b6f7e6-ad46-11e2-b27f-00144feabdc0.html |title=The Battle for Hastings |trans_title=黑斯廷斯战役 |work=[[金融时报_(英国)|金融时报]] |date=26 April 2013 |accessdate=6 August 2013 |archive-date=2016-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817021006/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/97b6f7e6-ad46-11e2-b27f-00144feabdc0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>：“想放纵的人，想在海边放纵的人……到黑斯廷斯来，结识更多的同道中人，享受更多的毒品和酒”，这引起了她的选民的不满。拉德回应说：“我对黑斯廷斯非常乐观。我对《金融时报》描述了一些黑斯廷斯众所周知的问题，但我也谈到了黑斯廷斯规模巨大的投资，下降的失业率，还说了许多积极的事情。”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theargus.co.uk/news/10391147.Sussex_MP_blasted_for_drugs_comment/ |title=Sussex MP blasted for drugs comment |trans_title=苏塞克斯的国会议员关于毒品的爆炸性评论 |work=The Argus |date=1 May 2013 |accessdate=6 August 2013 |archive-date=2018-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023120013/https://www.theargus.co.uk/news/10391147.Sussex_MP_blasted_for_drugs_comment/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

