ve-date=2020-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200214065414/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/10/01/revealed-amber-rudds-safe-sex-poetry-prize-that-found-a-rhyme-fo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

